<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 15:15:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>印度对中国产品和投资的打压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/indias-clampdown-chinese-products-investment-2024-10-21/</link><description>印度外交大臣维克拉姆·米斯里周一表示，印度和中国已就在有争议的喜马拉雅边境巡逻达成协议，旨在解决长达四年的军事对峙。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 12:54:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/indias-clampdown-chinese-products-investment-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>独家：欧盟将选择公司作为关键矿产联合购买平台</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/eu-set-choose-firm-critical-minerals-joint-buying-platform-2024-10-21/</link><description>文件显示，知情人士告诉路透社，欧盟正急于为关键矿产和能源制定一项耗资 900 万欧元的联合采购机制，正在八家竞标者中进行选择，争夺开发一个平台。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 12:47:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/eu-set-choose-firm-critical-minerals-joint-buying-platform-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>王毅表示，中方敦促日方保持“相互合作、互不威胁”的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-japan-maintain-mutually-cooperative-non-threatening-ties-says-wang-2024-10-21/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周一对日本国家安全顾问秋叶刚夫表示，中国希望日本与其共同努力，维持两国之间“相互合作、互不威胁”的立场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 12:17:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-japan-maintain-mutually-cooperative-non-threatening-ties-says-wang-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>解决中印边境对峙的漫长道路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/long-road-resolving-india-china-border-stand-off-2024-10-21/</link><description>印度周一表示，已与中国就两国共有争议的喜马拉雅边界沿线的巡逻安排达成协议，为解决 2020 年升级的冲突打开了大门。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:53:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/long-road-resolving-india-china-border-stand-off-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称富达国际在中国裁员500人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/fidelity-international-cuts-500-jobs-china-sources-say-2024-10-21/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，富达国际 (FIL) 将在其中国一家业务部门裁员约 500 人，这是近年来全球金融公司在全球第二大经济体进行的最大规模裁员。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:22:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/fidelity-international-cuts-500-jobs-china-sources-say-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买入：持有股票记录，黄金对冲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-21/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 10:13:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国蓬勃发展的灰色市场给奢侈品牌雪上加霜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-booming-grey-markets-add-woes-luxury-brands-2024-10-21/</link><description>中国的奢侈品二手市场和灰色市场正在蓬勃发展，在经济疲软的情况下，奢侈品牌的价格上涨促使一些消费者寻找更便宜的购买方式，加深了人们对路威酩轩集团(LVMH)等公司的担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 10:13:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-booming-grey-markets-add-woes-luxury-brands-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>肖尔茨表示，德国汽车制造商不应害怕中国的竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-carmakers-should-not-be-afraid-chinese-competition-says-scholz-2024-10-21/</link><description>德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨周一在梅赛德斯-奔驰首家电池回收工厂开业时表示，德国汽车制造商不应害怕来自中国的竞争，他称这项投资是德国新工业政策议程的一部分。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 10:07:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-carmakers-should-not-be-afraid-chinese-competition-says-scholz-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>马斯克将在业绩公布日接受有关特斯拉机器人出租车押注的质询</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/musk-face-questions-teslas-robotaxi-bets-results-day-2024-10-21/</link><description>特斯拉的投资者和分析师将有机会在周三就其自动驾驶出租车计划向首席执行官埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）进行拷问，届时这家电动汽车制造商将公布季度业绩。此前，本月特斯拉发布的季度业绩大肆宣传，但缺乏关键细节，导致股价遭受重挫。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 10:04:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/musk-face-questions-teslas-robotaxi-bets-results-day-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，印度考虑通过俄罗斯进口蒙古焦煤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-considers-imports-mongolian-coking-coal-via-russia-source-says-2024-10-21/</link><description>一位直接了解此事的高级政府官员表示，印度正在探索通过俄罗斯定期进口蒙古焦煤的方法，因为新德里试图避免过度依赖通过中国过境。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 09:45:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-considers-imports-mongolian-coking-coal-via-russia-source-says-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>印度外长表示，印度和中国达成解决边界冲突的协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-china-have-arrived-border-patrolling-pact-indias-top-diplomat-says-2024-10-21/</link><description>印度外交部长周一表示，印度和中国已就巡逻有争议的边境达成协议，以结束长达四年的军事对峙，为改善这两个亚洲大国之间的政治和商业关系铺平了道路。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 09:31:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-china-have-arrived-border-patrolling-pact-indias-top-diplomat-says-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>中信股份将以4.303亿美元出售麦当劳中国及香港业务股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/citic-sell-stake-mcdonalds-china-hong-kong-business-4303-mln-2024-10-21/</link><description>中国国有企业中信股份已同意以 4.303 亿美元的价格出售其在中国大陆和香港经营快餐连锁店麦当劳的公司 19.23% 的股份，全面退出该业务。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 09:30:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/citic-sell-stake-mcdonalds-china-hong-kong-business-4303-mln-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>国家开发银行原副行长因受贿被判有期徒刑12年并处罚金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-development-bank-former-vp-given-12-years-jail-fine-bribery-2024-10-21/</link><description>据中央电视台周一报道，国家开发银行（CDB）前副行长王永胜因受贿罪被判处 12 年有期徒刑，并处罚金 200 万元人民币（28 万美元）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 09:19:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-development-bank-former-vp-given-12-years-jail-fine-bribery-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>中方谴责缅甸总领事馆遇袭事件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-condemns-attack-myanmar-consulate-2024-10-21/</link><description>中国外交部发言人表示，中国谴责周一针对中国驻曼德勒领事馆的袭击，并敦促缅甸当局尽一切努力逮捕肇事者。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 08:06:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-condemns-attack-myanmar-consulate-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>台湾任命总统顾问为APEC峰会代表</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-appoints-presidential-advisor-apec-summit-representative-2024-10-21/</link><description>台湾总统府周一表示，已任命赖清德总统的一名高级顾问作为今年秘鲁亚太经合组织峰会的特使，这是台湾和中国大陆共同参加的少数国际论坛之一。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 07:35:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-appoints-presidential-advisor-apec-summit-representative-2024-10-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>